Package com.deco2800.game.ai.tasks

Class DefaultMultiTask

java.lang.Object
com.deco2800.game.ai.tasks.DefaultTask
com.deco2800.game.ai.tasks.DefaultMultiTask
All Implemented Interfaces:
Task
Direct Known Subclasses:
WanderTask
public abstract class DefaultMultiTask
extends DefaultTask
implements Task
A default task implementation that stores the associated entity and updates status when starting/stopping a task. Removes some boilerplate code from each task. Includes a method for switching the current task for more intricate tasks.
